title: True Miami Vice (2006) Soundtrack
description:
Soundtrack to the drama thriller &#039;Miami Vice&#039; (2006), Michael Mann&#039;s film version of the seminal 80s police series. Also includes the instrumental version of the Jay-Z and Linkin Park collaboration &#039;Numb/Encore&#039;, used in the theatrical trailers.

All tracks in MP3 format, mostly at 320 k.b.p.s.. Please note that this compilation varies from the official C.D. soundtrack release.
